{"tid":160342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]天橋車禍火燒車　司機當場燒死另4人傷","createTime":"2017-03-17T15:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T16:19:37.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84cc1a8a88fdbc35a145fbd0ff7f0026e695a0cf","tid":160342,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:42:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tw.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170317/bkncn-20170317001548004-0317_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170317%2Fbkncn-20170317001548004-0317_05011_001.html&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=805edcec\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170317/bkncn-20170317001548004-0317_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170317/photo/bkncn-20170317001548004-0317_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170317%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170317001548004-0317_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=424a0483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江西南昌老福山高架天橋昨晚發生致命車禍，共有6車相撞，其中2車起火焚燒，1人被當場燒死，另有4人受傷送院。車禍原因仍有待當局調查。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，車禍起因是肇事私家車突然失控，撞向另一輛私家車，其後再撞向對面線的其他車輛。肇事私家車起火焚燒，司機當場被燒死；從後而至有數輛車亦因收掣不及，發生輕微碰撞。<br />\n<br />\n從網上片段所見，車禍發生後現場情況慘烈，火光熊熊，更接連傳出爆炸聲，橋上欄杆亦被撞毀，期間有路過的市民不顧個人安危，上前救出多名被困車內人員。目前交警、消防等相關人員已趕到現場處理，並用拖車運走燒成廢鐵的肇事私家車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9dfd31f40bd5d6044996a120c840df9f5f00cd","tid":160342,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"火燒支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa8aa425a0158c0deb61e4af7c86d78b547843d","tid":160342,"uid":90135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}